
     Attached please find clean copies of the LV Cogen Agreement and
Exhibits. The Agreement incorporates my changes as well as Dale's and
incorporates the site specific performance guarantees.  The blackline of
the agreement shows changes made form the original form agreed to by GE.
The blackline of the exhibits is against the version I received last
night from Dale.

