4. The information regarding notices in sections 25.1 and 25.3.

Pursuant to earlier conversations on other agreements, I have removed
the reference to Exhibits N-1 and N-3 and included actual amounts in the
text of the Agreement.


To finalize the exhibits, we need the following:

1. Do we need anything in Section B of Schedule A-1?

2. Exhibits B-1 (Specification), H-2 (Training) and R (Schedule of
Witness Test Points) need to be provided.

3. Please confirm for Exhibit T, that ENA has received all
information that it should have received.

4. To the extent required, we need a Seller Parent Guaranty for
Exhibit C-1.


